---
import DefaultLayout from "../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro"
---

<DefaultLayout>
  <div slot="nav">
    <header class="hidden lg:flex 2xl:hidden flex-col text-[0.65rem] leading-none tracking-tight border border-black mb-10 font-sans uppercase">
      <div class="flex border-b border-black">
        <a href="https://github.com/robo-korgi" class="w-1/2 text-center px-4 py-2 border-r border-black">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://soundcloud.com/robo-korgi" class="w-1/2 text-center px-4 py-2">Soundcloud</a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-[1.0625rem] font-bold py-3 border-b border-black">ROBO-KORGI</div>
      <div class="flex">
        <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/robokorgi" class="w-1/2 text-center px-4 py-2 border-r border-black">Twitch</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@robo-korgi" class="w-1/2 text-center px-4 py-2">YouTube</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <header class="flex lg:hidden 2xl:flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between text-[0.65rem] leading-none tracking-tight border border-black mb-10 font-sans uppercase">
      <div class="flex justify-center sm:justify-start border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-black w-full sm:w-auto">
        <a href="https://github.com/robo-korgi" class="px-4 py-2 sm:px-5 sm:py-2 border-r border-black">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://soundcloud.com/robo-korgi" class="px-4 py-2 sm:px-5 sm:py-2">Soundcloud</a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-[1.0625rem] font-bold py-3 sm:py-0 flex-grow border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-none">ROBO-KORGI</div>
      <div class="flex justify-center sm:justify-end border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-black w-full sm:w-auto">
        <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/robokorgi" class="px-4 py-2 sm:px-5 sm:py-2 border-r border-black">Twitch</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@robo-korgi" class="px-4 py-2 sm:px-5 sm:py-2">YouTube</a>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto md:mx-0 px-4 md:px-0">
    <div class="text-left text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-[#0d0d0d] font-russo">
      robo-korgi<span class="inline-block ml-[0.1875rem] align-baseline">©</span>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-base md:text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed tracking-normal text-[#222]">
      creating kinda ok digital content<br />
      hopefully making the world a little less worse.
    </p>

    <strong class="block mt-6 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-3 font-russo uppercase text-[#0d0d0d]">
      CODER, STREAMER, AUTIST, DREAMER
    </strong>

    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#222]">
      I started making bad lofi music under the name robo-korgi a few years back. Now, the robo-korgi digital empire also includes Fortnite highlight vids and Twitch live-coding app development livestreams. I found out recently (in my 40s, because why not) that:
    </p>

    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-4 mb-4 ml-4 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#222]">
      <li>I'm autistic</li>
      <li>I have ADHD</li>
      <li>U.S. democracy is likely collapsing, and</li>
      <li>Humanity will probably lose the climate fight — and has already begun to lose.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#222]">
      (I'm not a doomer; I just don't think pretending helps.) So I'll blog about those uplifting topics a bit.
    </p>
  </div>
</DefaultLayout>
